high_descs: Turn left and go straight towards the wall. Then, hang left and walk straight into the room and turn to the bath tub on your right.
Pick up tomato from the bath tub.
Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the sink.
Place tomato on the bath tub.
Turn around and walk to the bathtub to your left.
Pick up tomato from the bath tub.
Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the sink.

high_descs: Go into the bedroom straight ahead, then take the right and go straight into the bathroom.
Pick up the close tomato from inside the bathtub.
Look to the sink to your right.
Put the tomato down in the sink.
Turn back to the bathtub.
Pick up the second tomato from the tub.
Look back to the sink.
Put the second tomato next to the first one.
anns.task_desc: Move two tomatoes from a tub to a sink.
